N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 112.2 - Land requirements

State Regulations

Site index (site quality index based on total height of
dominant trees at 50 years of age) will be given on each packet of seed, if
available. Elevation of place from which seed was collected will be shown on
each packet of seed. Notes
